{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "22", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "04", "M": "36", "S": "34"}}, "news": [{"title": "Delhi: DDA informs NGT it will complete O zone drone survey in two months", "para": "Delhi Development Authority will finish a drone survey of the Yamuna floodplain in two months. This survey covers 165 square kilometers. DDA has already removed encroachments from seven acres. The survey is part of efforts to document the O zone. Authorities are monitoring for further illegal constructions. Police have been directed to prevent unauthorized building within the zone.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/dda-to-complete-o-zone-drone-survey-in-two-months-aims-to-address-river-pollution/130431373?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-43344/130431373.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Andhra Pradesh government offers 50% VLT relief to boost construction activity", "para": "Property owners in the state will now benefit from a 50% discount on vacant land tax during construction. This policy shift, effective from construction commencement until occupancy certificate issuance, aims to stimulate building activity and alleviate financial pressure. Officials emphasized this move will encourage timely project completion and better land utilization across urban areas.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/andhra-pradesh-government-offers-50-vlt-relief-to-boost-construction-activity/130431263?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-93936/130431263.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Telangana launches first land registration with survey map under Bhu Bharati", "para": "On Tuesday, the first land registration with a survey map was completed in Kusumanchi